<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=4 -->
(a) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Formal applications, amendments and notifications.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Except as provided in paragraph (b) of this section, applications, amendments and notifications must be filed using
the standard forms listed in paragraph (c) of this section.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(b) 
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=3 -->
Informal applications, amendments and notifications.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Applications, amendments and notifications in letter or document form may be accepted for filing, if none of the standard
forms listed in this section are prescribed for or clearly applicable for the intended purpose. Such informal applications,
amendments and notifications must be submitted in duplicate, with a caption clearly stating the name of the filer,
nature of the filing, the Public Mobile service involved, the call sign of the relevant existing station, if any, and
the file number of the relevant pending application, if any, and must contain all necessary technical data and exhibits.
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

